  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you make your way through an underground megastructure, you fall into an area with a long-lasting power outage. Your only way forward is to find a path towards the elevator, in the surrounding darkness, which will lead you to a higher level. Hopefully leading out of this place. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tread the pitch black corridors of the structure, and try to find your way out. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use various devices at your disposal, to illuminate the darkness. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the torch to illuminate your close surroundings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw flares to create a mobile source of light</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place beacons to mark your way </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the elevator and use it to travel from one floor to another. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve problems preventing your journey, and continue onwards. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COLLECTIBLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some levels contain collectible upgrades for the player characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you make your way through an underground megastructure, you fall into an area with a long-lasting power outage. Your only way forward is to find a path towards the elevator, in the surrounding darkness, which will lead you to a higher level. Hopefully leading out of this place. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tread the pitch black corridors of the structure, and try to find your way out. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use various devices at your disposal, to illuminate the darkness. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the torch to illuminate your close surroundings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw flares to create a mobile source of light</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place beacons to mark your way </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the elevator and use it to travel from one floor to another. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve problems preventing your journey, and continue onwards. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COLLECTIBLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some levels contain collectible upgrades for the player characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
